2026-05-17T00:11:01.9086186Z 246            Harden Google Play Billing's proxy activities so the system
2026-05-17T00:11:01.9087050Z 247            cannot restore them from Recents or after process death with a
2026-05-17T00:11:01.9087949Z 248            stale Intent. The library's onCreate reads the PendingIntent
2026-05-17T00:11:01.9089286Z 249            extra without null-checking; if Android recreates the activity
2026-05-17T00:11:01.9090069Z 250            and the extra is missing, it NPEs on
2026-05-17T00:11:01.9090866Z 251            PendingIntent.getIntentSender(). noHistory + excludeFromRecents
2026-05-17T00:11:01.9091810Z 252            finishes the activity as soon as it leaves the foreground so it
2026-05-17T00:11:01.9092682Z 253            is never re-entered with a missing extra. Library 8.x adds its
2026-05-17T00:11:01.9093546Z 254            own configChanges absorber and a v2 proxy, both of which we
2026-05-17T00:11:01.9094286Z 255            preserve via tools:node="merge".
