2026-05-17T00:11:02.2572457Z 271            Harden Google Play Billing's proxy activities so the system
2026-05-17T00:11:02.2572817Z 272            cannot restore them from Recents or after process death with a
2026-05-17T00:11:02.2573158Z 273            stale Intent. The library's onCreate reads the PendingIntent
2026-05-17T00:11:02.2573509Z 274            extra without null-checking; if Android recreates the activity
2026-05-17T00:11:02.2573746Z 275            and the extra is missing, it NPEs on
2026-05-17T00:11:02.2574159Z 276            PendingIntent.getIntentSender(). noHistory + excludeFromRecents
2026-05-17T00:11:02.2574517Z 277            finishes the activity as soon as it leaves the foreground so it
2026-05-17T00:11:02.2574855Z 278            is never re-entered with a missing extra. Library 8.x adds its
2026-05-17T00:11:02.2575584Z 279            own configChanges absorber and a v2 proxy, both of which we
